coursera_azure_vm_july04   Azure: Create a Virtual Machine and Deploy a Web Server. 

By the end of this guided project, you will be able to understand how the basic networking architecture in Azure works, 
by creating Virtual Networks, subnets, security groups and Virtual Machines. You will also learn how to use Bastion 
to connect to a Linux machine using SSH without exposing and external IP. 
You'll also learn how to expose a public IP and an HTTPS port to access your web server.
